Herdwick Cottages is a family-run holiday cottage letting business based in Kendal, Cumbria. We offer an ever-growing choice of cottages and apartments to rent, as well as glamping units and lodges across the Lake District and Yorkshire Dales.

Holiday Cottages in the Lake District are an excellent option for UK-based holidays, especially for couples, families and groups of friends. It offers spectacular scenery, beautiful attractions, and many fell walks that offer majestic views! Herdwick Cottages offers holiday accommodation across Windermere, Ambleside, Kendal, Kirkby Lonsdale, Ulverston, Buttermere, Cockermouth, Sedbergh, Eden Valley, Penrith & Ullswater.

There, you will find water sports, land sports, adrenaline activities, festivals and pretty much everything else to meet guests’ needs – plus a fantastic choice of award-winning restaurants, pubs and cafes!

Booking through Herdwick Cottages will give you the peace of mind that comes with using a reputable agent who always puts the customer first.

Herdwick Cottages Supports the Great North Air Ambulance Service

We are also pleased to support the Great North Air Ambulance Service by allowing guests to add a voluntary donation when booking. For each £1 donated, we will donate the same!
